Declare an array: //allocate the name for a variable
int[] numbers;

Create an array;//allocate the memory for a variable
int[] numbers=new int[10];
numbers.length method will return the length of the array
array of arrays:
int[][] grid;
multidimensional array:
int[,] grid= new int[5,4];
grid.GetLength(0);//will return the length of the first index

